0"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault was detected from 2025-06-11T09:10:43Z to 2025-06-11T09:26:43Z. Please analyze its root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-11 09:10:43+00:00 to 2025-06-11 09:26:43+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["checkoutservice-1", "emailservice-1", "productcatalogservice-1", "recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["shippingservice-2", "frontend-0", "adservice-0", "recommendationservice-1", "paymentservice-1", "cartservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["checkoutservice-0", "frontend-2", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-2", "currencyservice-0", "cartservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["emailservice-2", "productcatalogservice-0", "checkoutservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "frontend-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-2", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2", "redis-cart-0"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes", "node_memory_usage_rate", "pod_cpu_usage", "rrt", "rrt_max"], "log_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [],\n  \"hypotheses\": []\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据分析工具的结果，我们识别到了以下显著的异常调用链和相关指标：\n\n1. **Node 异常**：\n   - `node_memory_usage_rate` 和 `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes` - 节点 `aiops-k8s-03` 和 `aiops-k8s-04` 出现内存使用率升高，内存可用量减少。\n\n2. **Pod 异常**：\n   - `redis-cart-0` 的 `pod_cpu_usage` 在 fault_p99 增加到较高值，显示 CPU 使用率异常，但因变化不显著，初步暂不作为高优先级。\n   \n3. **Service 性能问题**：\n   - `shippingservice-0` 在 `rrt_max` 和 `rrt` 上都出现显著增加，特别是 `rrt_max` 在 fault_p99 中激增。\n   - `emailservice-2` 和 `currencyservice-0` 的 `rrt_max` 变化较显著，但未直接关联系统级别故障。\n\n### JSON 输出\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"node_memory_usage_rate\",\n    \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-03\",\n      \"reason\": \"节点内存使用率升高，导致系统性能可能下降\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate 从正常 Median 46.75 到故障 Median 55.48\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-04\",\n      \"reason\": \"节点内存可用量减少，可能影响服务质量\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes 从正常 p99 12043833958.4 到故障 p99 10654001766.4\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"服务响应时间显著增加，表明性能问题\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max 从正常 p99 10648.0 到故障 p99 69918.65\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod CPU 使用略增，但变化不显著\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage 在 fault_p99 从 0.08 到 0.12\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n此输出初步说明潜在资源瓶颈与性能问题。随后可以进行更深入的分析以验证这些可能的问题。", "trace_analysis_findings": "## 初始扫描分析报告\n\n### 概述\n在 2025-06-11T09:10:43Z 到 2025-06-11T09:26:43Z 期间发现了异常调用链。通过 trace 数据的分析，我们发现了以下显著异常调用链：\n\n### 异常调用链发现\n- **checkoutservice->cartservice (POST /hipstershop.CartService/EmptyCart)**\n  - **Normal Avg Duration:** 2569.20 ms\n  - **Anomaly Avg Duration:** 29031.00 ms\n  - **延迟倍数:** 11.3\n  - **Hypotheses:** CartService由于Redis的调用异常导致延迟\n\n- **checkoutservice->cartservice (POST /hipstershop.CartService/AddItem)**\n  - **Normal Avg Duration:** 3869.86 ms\n  - **Anomaly Avg Duration:** 29290.00 ms\n  - **延迟倍数:** 7.6\n  - **Hypotheses:** CartService被checkoutservice异常调用导致延迟增大\n\n- **checkoutservice->paymentservice (hipstershop.PaymentService/Charge)**\n  - **Normal Avg Duration:** 12831.39 ms\n  - **Anomaly Avg Duration:** 79303.00 ms\n  - **延迟倍数:** 6.18\n  - **Hypotheses:** paymentservice处理支付请求异常导致延迟\n\n- **checkoutservice->shippingservice (hipstershop.ShippingService/ShipOrder)**\n  - **Normal Avg Duration:** 9347.60 ms\n  - **Anomaly Avg Duration:** 43158.00 ms\n  - **延迟倍数:** 4.62\n  - **Hypotheses:** ShippingService处理发货请求异常导致延迟\n\n- **redis->cartservice (HMSET)**\n  - **Normal Avg Duration:** 1573.06 ms\n  - **Anomaly Avg Duration:** 8872.13 ms\n  - **延迟倍数:** 5.64\n  - **Hypotheses:** Redis的异常调用可能导致cartservice的延迟增大\n\n### 根因分析\n根据以上调用链数据，以下组件或调用可能是延迟增加的根本原因：\n\n1. **CartService**: 调用 Redis 时发生异常，影响 CheckoutService 的请求。\n2. **PaymentService**: Charge 操作延迟显著增大，可能导致支付请求处理瓶颈。\n3. **ShippingService**: GetQuote 和 ShipOrder 消息处理时间延长，影响结算流程。\n\n由于这些异常调用链中没有明确的错误状态码组合，我们只分析了延迟倍数来识别延迟瓶颈。\n\n### JSON 输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"redis->cartservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CartService 的 EmptyCart 延迟由正常 2569 ms 增加到异常 29031 ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PaymentService 的 Charge 操作延迟由正常 12831 ms 增加到异常 79303 ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"ShippingService 的 ShipOrder 延迟由正常 9347.6 ms 增加到异常 43158 ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Redis 的 HMSET 操作延迟由正常 1573 ms 增加到异常 8872 ms\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n通过此分析报告，我们已经标记了显著的异常调用链和延迟瓶颈。如需更详细的错误状态码分析，可以进一步获取异常状态码的组合。"}
