ration:** 2569.20 ms\n  - **Anomaly Avg Duration:** 29031.00 ms\n  - **延迟倍数:** 11.3\n  - **Hypotheses:** CartService由于Redis的调用异常导致延迟\n\n- **checkoutservice->cartservice (POST /hipstershop.CartService/AddItem)**\n  - **Normal Avg Duration:** 3869.86 ms\n  - **Anomaly Avg Duration:** 29290.00 ms\n  - **延迟倍数:** 7.6\n  - **Hypotheses:** CartService被checkoutservice异常调用导致延迟增大\n\n- **checkoutservice->paymentservice (hipstershop.PaymentService/Charge)**\n  - **Normal Avg Duration:** 12831.39 ms\n  - **Anomaly Avg Duration:** 79303.00 ms\n  - **延迟倍数:** 6.18\n  - **Hypotheses:** paymentservice处理支付请求异常导致延迟\n\n- **checkoutservice->shippingservice (hipstershop.ShippingService/ShipOrder)**\n  - **Normal Avg Duration:** 9347.60 ms\n  - **Anomaly Avg Duration:** 43158.00 ms\n  - **延迟倍数:** 4.62\n  - **Hypotheses:** ShippingService处理发货请求异常导致延迟\n\n- **redis->cartservice (HMSET)**\n  - **Normal Avg Duration:** 1573.06 ms\n  - **Anomaly Avg Duration:** 8872.13 ms\n  - **延迟倍数:** 5.64\n  - **Hypotheses:** Redis的异常调用可能导致cartservice的延迟增大\n\n### 根因分析\n根据以上调用链数据，以下组件或调用可能是延迟增加的根本原因：\n\n1. **CartService**: 调用 Redis 时发生异常，影响 CheckoutService 的请求。\n2. **PaymentService**: Charge 操作延迟显著增大，可能导致支付请求处理瓶颈。\n3. **ShippingService**: GetQuote 和 ShipOrder 消息处理时间延长，影响结算流程。\n\n由于这些异常调用链中没有明确的错误状态码组合，我们只分析了延迟倍数来识别延迟瓶颈。\n\n### JSON 输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"redis->cartservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CartService 的 EmptyCart 延迟由正常 2569 ms 增加到异常 29031 ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PaymentService 的 Charge 操作延迟由正常 12831 ms 增加到异常 79303 ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n    